data.description: Unleash your imagination and turn this house into your dream home. This 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom, 1,488 sq ft home built in 1977. With an attached 2-car garage, bonus storage space, a newer well, and 4.75 acres of wildlife-rich land, this property is brimming with potential. Make it yours today!
